## 🤝 Contributing

We welcome contributions! Please see our [Contributing Guide](CONTRIBUTING.md) for details.

### Development

```bash
# Install development dependencies
uv sync --dev

# Run tests
uv run pytest

# Run type checks
uv run mypy coda

# Format code
uv run black .
uv run ruff check --fix
```

